Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.09,0:00:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（轻音乐）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，您在上一节中学习了 HTML 的基础知识。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在是时候学习基础知识了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网络的第二种语言，那就是 CSS。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在，CSS 本质上就是为内容设置样式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用 HTML 编写的。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在本节中，我们将继续构建
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的项目，基本上添加了一些视觉样式。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还将学习一些理论概念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 CSS 后面，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以便您真正了解 CSS 的工作原理。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那时，一旦你开始编写自己的代码，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会真正知道你在做什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望这一切听起来真的很令人兴奋，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.41,0:00:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们开始吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.09,0:00:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(gentle music)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you learnt the basics of HTML in the last section.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so now it's time to learn the basics
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of the second language of the web, and that is CSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, CSS is essentially all about styling the content
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that we write in HTML.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so in this section, we will keep building
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,our project and basically add some visual styles to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will also learn some theoretical concepts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that are behind CSS,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so that you actually understand how CSS works.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this is really important
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because then, once you start writing your own code,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you will actually know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I hope all that sounds really exciting,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.41,0:00:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and so let's get started.